

## **4. Integration**
### **Key Concepts:**
- **Indefinite & Definite Integrals**  
- **Methods:**  
  - Substitution, Integration by Parts  
  - Partial Fractions, Trigonometric Integrals  
- **Applications:**  
  - Area under curves, Volume of revolution  
  - Line integrals (for GATE EC/EE)  

### **Study Resources:**
- **Video Lectures:**  
  - [Blackpenredpen - Integration Techniques](https://www.youtube.com/c/blackpenredpen)  
  - [NPTEL - Integral Calculus (IIT Bombay)](https://nptel.ac.in/courses/111/105/111105104/)  
- **Textbooks:**  
  - *Calculus* – Gilbert Strang (Ch. 5 & 7)  
  - *Higher Engineering Mathematics* – B.S. Grewal (Integration Chapter)  
- **Practice Problems:**  
  - [GATE PYQs on Integration](https://gateoverflow.in/questions/tagged/integration)  
  - [Integral-calculator.com (Practice Tool)](https://www.integral-calculator.com/)  

